{"tid":714871,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉欣48歲生日　收兩層高玫瑰花勁冧","createTime":"2018-06-24T03:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T09:45:35.000Z","uid":48905,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"aa15ce1fda0ce974a8d84ab82189810211737c4e","tid":714871,"uid":48905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:53:10.000Z","msg":"今日係大美人李嘉欣（Michele）正日48歲生日，佢早前已獲得家人朋友為佢提早慶祝，食唔停口，認真開心！今日嘉欣喺社交網晒出一張個人照，相中見到布滿唔同寫住「Happy Birthday Michele」字眼嘅氣球，仲有一個兩層高嘅玫瑰花，有半個人咁高！上面仲用花圍咗個「M」字，張生日卡寫上「Queen M」，真係認真有意思，唔知係咪老公許晉亨送嘅驚喜呢？<br />\n<br />\n見嘉欣又笑不攏嘴，一面冧樣，大批網民都紛紛送上祝福，大讚佢依然美麗動人，「凍齡美女」嘅稱號當之無愧呀！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/24/115239_0df2629738faa592e62daa09208a60ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F24%2F115239_0df2629738faa592e62daa09208a60ed.jpg&h=cd2bc028&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5183ceee769e9d776f6a4f0a763e2c32fd0e2857","tid":714871,"uid":48905,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/16/012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F16%2F012045_9303f3c93486997d3fe247b1a80999d4.gif&h=74a0e790&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ee41f29c70b8f17df8e74199d376e69b8f4c634","tid":714871,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:59:06.000Z","msg":"好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e37304a511ab8d19ee986870d782c47620727d93","tid":714871,"uid":36296,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:02:26.000Z","msg":"睇錯兩高層送玫瑰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e874ebf1f9f57b2532fc9126f10d44c46ce0b870","tid":714871,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5183ceee769e9d776f6a4f0a763e2c32fd0e2857","